Old John doesn't keep many friends
Old John thinks he's a bad influence
Old John thinks he hurts those close
Old John thinks he's doing good
Old John realizes he's being narcissistic
Old John sees he's being self important
Old John asks "what if I'm not?"
Old John panics when his friends don't reply
Old John knows that he needs people
Old John believes he cares for them
Old John asks "what if I really don't?"
Old John wants to text his old friends
Old John does text his old friends
Old John stops replying after a couple days
Old John knows he should text back
Old John asks "And if I stop again?"
Old John ...


